channel.title: =====click here if you know javac well======
channel.description: hey i downloaded jdk 0.6 offline installation. I downloaded it to the c drive in program files. Now since i am done downloading it i went to my computer and clicked properties. I went to the advance tab. Then i clicked environment variables. I selected new and typed in my location of jdk. And now i compiled my server and it said "you do not have jdk 5.0 or 6.0 press any key to continue...." Why does it say that when i did everything i was suppose to do?
